{"tid":2034765,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Off the Record、Swing 強硬回擊　再度向攻擊 IZ*ONE 的惡意網民提告","createTime":"2020-05-25T12:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T13:22:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"083450e1fbc81610a226d9174ed4fc534f13b3b8","tid":2034765,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"一如許多經紀公司近年來的作法，經紀公司 Off the Record 和 Swing Entertainment 也在今天公開表示將對保護 IZ*ONE、對惡意網民提出告訴！<br />\n<br />\n目前共同負責 IZ*ONE 經紀事務的 Off the Record 和 Swing Entertainment 在今天（25 日）發出聲明，說明已經在去年 11 月向侮辱、誹謗 IZ*ONE，或散播有關成員之不實謠言而涉及毀損名譽者提告。<br />\n<br />\n儘管 Off the Record 和 Swing Entertainment 當時並未特別公開此事，僅低調地採取法律行動，但最近他們發現網路上的各種惡意言論依舊猖獗，因此決定為了保護 IZ*ONE 並根絕惡意貼文，而採取更強硬的法律手段，目前正準備展開第二次告訴。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，IZ*ONE 預定於 6 月 15 日帶著第三張迷你專輯回歸，Off the Record 和 Swing Entertainment 在聲明最後也表示：「感謝所有喜愛 IZ*ONE 的人，我們會繼續全力以赴來保護她們，也請大家像過去一樣給予溫暖的鼓勵和支持。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：Off the Record、Swing Entertainment）"},{"pid":"8a34f9501bd9422b63efb76afaffeac1f0ab8272","tid":2034765,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂台某啲會然要小心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41cdde2a319ba09593151b5f77bdb365abeb65e","tid":2034765,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/8f8716ccd07dc6454892e9740d01fbf3/ee85eb57935415e0-ce/s640x960/1517e24316b110fd2308464f3d724b7f49af885a.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F8f8716ccd07dc6454892e9740d01fbf3%2Fee85eb57935415e0-ce%2Fs640x960%2F1517e24316b110fd2308464f3d724b7f49af885a.gifv&h=95c51a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/a94f1be57c5de19d8b85e929500bc25e/ee85eb57935415e0-80/s640x960/